=== Etymology ===
From Latin ''gaudium'' meaning "joy" via French.

== [[adjective]] ==
#happy, joyful and lively.
#bright and colorful.
#homosexual. See [[queer]].
#typical of homosexual appearance or behavior. 
#''Slang''. figuratively used to describe something that is boring, unappealing, bad or rubbish.


== [[noun]] ==
#a homosexual, most often a male homosexual but sometimes applied to female homosexuals

